<lb n="0330b02" ed="T"/>野帝<note n="0330035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔十二〕－【明】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0330035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十二【大】，〔－〕【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330035"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">十二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0329035"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline"><note n="0330036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十三引＝引十二【明】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0330036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十三引【大】，引十二【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330036"><lem wit="【大】">十三引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">引十二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0330b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0330b0301">誦此真言必速應驗。問未來善惡一切災<note n="0330037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">祥＋（事）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0330037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祥【大】，祥事【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330037"><lem wit="【大】">祥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">祥事</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0330b04" ed="T"/>若不語或語遲。則結棒印。</p>
<lb n="0330b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0330b0501">二手合掌。二無名指外<note n="0330038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">支＝叉【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0330038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">支【大】，叉【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330038"><lem wit="【大】">支</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">叉</rdg></app>。二中指並立。二
<lb n="0330b06" ed="T"/>頭指各鉤無名指頭。二大指各令押中交。誦
<lb n="0330b07" ed="T"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0330b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0330b0801" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>母那誐<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0330010"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">二合二</rdg></app></note>都嚕都嚕<note place="inline">三</note>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀
<lb n="0330b09" ed="T"/><note n="0330039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引四〕－【明】【丙】</note><note n="0330039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引四【大】，〔－〕【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330039"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0330b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0330b1001">結此棒印。則<note n="0330040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">語＝諮【丙】</note><note n="0330040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">語【大】，諮【丙】</note><app n="0330040"><lem wit="【大】">語</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">諮</rdg></app>問種種事已。以大印真言加
<lb n="0330b11" ed="T"/>持閼伽。三灑童女面。即結解。此使者真言
<lb n="0330b12" ed="T"/>先應誦一萬遍則法成。則見身來。須獻閼伽
<lb n="0330b13" ed="T"/>乞願。願聖者一切處一切時使用皆辦。則隱
<lb n="0330b14" ed="T"/>不現。已後欲使。塗一小壇著香花飲食。誦真
<lb n="0330b15" ed="T"/>言一百八遍。則現身。則言龍宮中取長年藥
<lb n="0330b16" ed="T"/>如意寶珠。或使夜摩王處。延命增益壽命。或
<lb n="0330b17" ed="T"/>使<note n="0330041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（天）＋上【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0330041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，天上【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330041"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">天上</rdg></app>取妙甘露。或使他國問其善惡。亦能助
<lb n="0330b18" ed="T"/>軍陣摧破他敵。種種使用悉能成辦。此法一
<lb n="0330b19" ed="T"/>切迦樓羅法中最殊勝。祕密難得。汝當揀擇
<lb n="0330b20" ed="T"/>法器堪傳授者而傳與。<note n="0330042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">非人器人＝之若傳非器人【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0330042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">非人器人【大】，之若傳非器人【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330042"><lem wit="【大】">非人器人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">之若傳非器人</rdg></app>即損他。已
<lb n="0330b21" ed="T"/>後此法不成。是故應極祕密勿妄傳<note n="0330043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝授【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0330043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，授【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330043"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">授</rdg></app>之。大
<lb n="0330b22" ed="T"/>自在天迦樓羅陀羅尼曰。</p>
